| Stage                             | Description                                                               | Agentic Role                                |
| --------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| 1. Ingestion                      | Real-time feed intake from Thomson Reuters (e.g. Regulatory Intelligence) | **Feed Ingestion Agent**                    |
| 2. Risk Rating                    | Determine Materiality & Magnitude (M\&M) of regulatory change             | **Risk Assessment Agent**                   |
| 3. Triage                         | Regulatory Change Manager reviews high-risk items                         | **Triage Agent + Human in the Loop (HITL)** |
| 4. Impact Assessment              | Officers assess process, policy, control, and system impact               | **Impact Analysis Agent**                   |
| 5. Change Ownership & Action Plan | Assign task owners, timelines, resource plan                              | **Change Assignment Agent**                 |
| 6. Implementation Monitoring      | Track implementation milestones and updates                               | **Execution Tracker Agent**                 |
| 7. Regulatory Feedback            | Update regulator or internal audit systems post-change                    | **Regulator Communication Agent**           |


+-------------------+
| Regulatory Feeds  | <-- from Thomson Reuters, LexisNexis, etc.
+-------------------+
          |
          v
+-----------------------+
| Feed Ingestion Agent  | --> Extracts entity, date, geography, law
+-----------------------+
          |
          v
+------------------------+
| Risk Assessment Agent  | --> LLM + rules engine does initial M&M tagging
+------------------------+
          |
          v
+------------------------+
| Triage Agent           | --> Escalates high-risk to human change manager
+------------------------+
          |
          v
+-------------------------+
| Impact Analysis Agent   | --> Gathers process/IT/policy impact areas
| + Retrieve ISDA clauses |
+-------------------------+
          |
          v
+------------------------+
| Change Assignment Agent| --> Assigns change to departments or owners
+------------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------------+
| Execution Tracker Agent  | --> Reminds, updates, verifies milestones
+--------------------------+
          |
          v
+----------------------------+
| Regulator Communication Agent | --> Drafts notifications or disclosures
+----------------------------+




| Manual Task                                                | Agentic Process                                   | LLM Value                                     |
| ---------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Manually parsing PDFs of regulations                       | Feed Agent + PDF OCR + LLM summarization          | Extracts core change in simple form           |
| Risk tagging based on subjective judgment                  | Risk Agent with training data                     | Consistent rating based on context            |
| Searching for applicable clauses (e.g. in ISDA agreements) | Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) + Embeddings | Finds relevant contract clauses automatically |
| Email or memo drafting to teams/regulators                 | LLM auto-drafted updates, editable                | 90% draft-ready content                       |
| Tracking tasks via Excel                                   | Execution Agent integrates with Jira, Teams       | Proactive updates and escalation              |
| Regulatory mapping to policies or systems                  | Impact Agent trained on policy-doc embedding      | Suggests impact surface                       |




